\f0\b not
\f1\b0  
\f0\b rare
\f1\b0  in the Stafford\
       County, VA \uc0\u8594  Madison County, KY corridor. The family's presence is\
       extremely well established in both locations and in early Illinois\
       (Edgar County). This migration corridor matches perfectly with what you\
       know about Stephen and Polly ending up in Clay County, IL.\
