\f1\b0  
\f0\b documented
\f1\b0  
\f0\b link
\f1\b0  in any currently accessible public\
        genealogical record explicitly naming Stephen Coy as the son of\
       Christopher Coy. The connection appears to come from family trees in\
       databases like Ancestry and FamilySearch, which are sometimes built on\
       inference rather than primary sources.\
