\f0\b What
\f1\b0  
\f0\b this
\f1\b0  
\f0\b suggests:
\f1\b0  There were multiple Coy households in Madison\
       County, KY in 1817 and a Coy elder (Christopher) settled in Lawrence\
       County, IL by the 1820s\'961830s. This is consistent with an extended\
       family cluster making the VA \uc0\u8594  KY \u8594  southern IL migration together or in\
        close succession. Stephen settling in Clay County (adjacent to Lawrence\
        County, where Christopher died) fits a pattern of following a family\
       anchor.\
